text: El clásico () is a 2015 Iraqi-Norwegian drama film directed by Halkawt Mustafa. It was selected as the Iraqi entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 89th Academy Awards but it was not nominated. ==Cast== * Wrya Ahmed as Alan * Dana Ahmes as Shirwan * Kamaran Raoof as Jalal * Rozhin Sharifi as Gona ==See also== * List of submissions to the 89th Academy Awards for Best Foreign Language Film * List of Iraqi submissions for the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film * Kurdish cinema ==References== ==External links== * Category:2015 films Category:2015 drama films Category:Iraqi films Category:Norwegian films Category:Norwegian drama films Category:Kurdish- language films
title: El clásico (film)
